    "duration": "3:34",
    "audience": [
      "Adults"
    ],
    "description": "You do not need to justify your time. You only need to define your own. So you respond with clarity. This is what works for me. You do not over-explain. You do not negotiate your availability around theirs. You set your position. Something shifts. The dynamic becomes more balanced. Because you are no longer reinforcing the imbalance. You notice something else. You almost adjusted again. You felt the pull to accommodate without limit. But you recognised it before it became your behavior. That is the shift. You are no longer someone who absorbs perceived status through busyness. You are becoming someone who defines their own position… regardless of how others present theirs. Busyness does not define value. Clarity does.",
